OL,3,CInexperienced climbers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom climbing Everest following
OL,5,Ctraffic jams
OL,7,FInexperienced climbers could be barred
OL,8,Ffrom trying to climb Mount Everest,
OL,9,Fthanks to a new law being proposed in
OL,10,FNepal.
OL,12,FUnder the new legislation,
OL,13,Fmountaineers would need to have
OL,14,Fsuccessfully summited a peak in Nepal
OL,15,Fabove 7,000 metres to obtain a permit
OL,16,Fto climb the world's tallest mountain,
OL,17,Fwhich stands at 8,849 metres.
