OL,3,CInexperienced climbers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom climbing Everest following
OL,5,Ctraffic jams
OL,7,FIt comes at a time when the climb to
OL,8,Fthe top of Everest is more popular
OL,9,Fthan ever, with thrill-seeking
OL,10,Finfluencers taking on the summit and
OL,11,Fsharing their climbs on social media.
OL,13,FThe new rule aims to tackle concerns
OL,14,Faround the environment and the welfare
OL,15,Fof climbers, and is part of Nepal's
OL,16,FIntegrated Tourism Bill, which is
OL,17,Fbeing debated at a time when
OL,18,Fovercrowding is a growing concern.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
