OL,4,Cfrom climbing Everest following
OL,5,Ctraffic jams
OL,7,FEverest sits within the Himalayas, a
OL,8,Fvast mountain range stretching 2,400
OL,9,Fkilometres across six Asian countries.
OL,11,FThe new law would require climbers to
OL,12,Fmeet specific insurance, health, age
OL,13,Fand experience thresholds before
OL,14,Fattempting the climb.
OL,16,FAccording to the Himalayan Database, a
OL,17,Fdigital archive of the mountain range,
OL,18,Fover 1,000 people attempted the climb
OL,19,Fto the summit last year.
