OL,7,FIn the same year, British climber
OL,8,FRobin Haynes Fisher reached the summit
OL,9,Fof Mount Everest but died after
OL,10,Ffalling ill on his descent.
OL,12,FThe 44-year-old, described by his
OL,13,Ffamily in a statement as an
OL,14,F"aspirational adventurer", wrote of
OL,15,Fhis concerns about overcrowding in his
OL,16,Ffinal Instagram post.
