OL,7,F2023 was one of the deadliest years on
OL,8,Frecord, with 18 confirmed deaths and
OL,9,Fan unprecedented number of rescues
OL,10,Ffrom the mountain.
OL,12,FThe Bill also proposes an
OL,13,Fenvironmental protection fund,
OL,14,Fdesigned to help remove decades of
OL,15,Frubbish build-up in the Himalayas.
OL,17,FEverest, nicknamed "The World's
OL,18,FHighest Garbage Dump", has long
OL,19,Fsuffered from problems with litter as
OL,20,Fa result of its visitors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
