OL,4,Cfrom climbing Everest following
OL,5,Ctraffic jams
OL,7,FAlthough the exact figure is unknown,
OL,8,Fit has been estimated that the world's
OL,9,Ftallest mountain is home to
OL,10,Fapproximately 50 tonnes of waste, with
OL,11,Fthe average climber producing around
OL,12,F12kg.
OL,14,FThis includes abandoned tents, cans
OL,15,Fand food packaging.
OL,17,FThe Bill will go to the House of
OL,18,FRepresentatives after Nepal's national
OL,19,Felections in March.
